Interface ChannelFormat

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AudioChannelFormat, SpectralChannelFormat

    public interface ChannelFormat
    The ChannelFormat is an interface base class for representing one channel of a multi-channel data set. It store the parameters which a channl might have. This is an abstratc class which other
    1. sample rate : the sample rate, specified as an int
    2. channel name : the name of this channel
